1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 { C44 Scotch Game } 3... exd4 (3... Nxd4 { Lolli Variation } 4. Nxd4 (4. Nxe5?! Ne6) 4... exd4 5. Qxd4 (5. Bc4 { Napoleon Gambit }) 5... Ne7 6. Nc3 Nc6 7. Qe3 Bb4) (3... Bd6 4. c3 Nf6) (3... d6?! 4. Bb5 (4. dxe5 Nxe5 (4... dxe5 5. Qxd8+ Kxd8) 5. Nxe5 dxe5 6. Qxd8+ Kxd8 7. Bc4) (4. d5) 4... Bd7 5. Nc3 exd4 6. Nxd4 g6) (3... d5?! 4. Nxe5 dxe4 5. Bb5 Bd7 6. Nxd7 Qxd7 7. d5 a6 8. dxc6 Qxd1+ 9. Kxd1 O-O-O+ 10. Ke2 axb5 11. cxb7+ Kxb7) 4. Nxd4 (4. Bc4 { Scotch Gambit } 4... Nf6 { Scotch Gambit/Dubois Reti Defense } (4... Bc5 { Haxo Gambit } 5. c3 Nf6 6. cxd4 { C54 Italian Game: Classical Variation/Greco Gambit/Traditional Line } 6... Bb4+ 7. Bd2 Bxd2+ 8. Nbxd2 d5 9. exd5 Nxd5) (4... d6 5. Nxd4 Nf6 6. Nc3) (4... Bb4+ { Scotch Gambit/London Defense } 5. c3 dxc3 6. O-O cxb2 7. Bxb2 Nf6 8. a3 Be7 9. Ng5 { [%cal Gc4f7,Gg5f7] } 9... O-O) (4... Be7 { Benima Defense } 5. Nxd4 Nf6 6. Nxc6 dxc6 7. Qxd8+ Bxd8) (4... g6 5. Nxd4 Bg7 6. Nxc6 bxc6 7. O-O Ne7) 5. e5 { Scotch Gambit/Advance Variation } (5. O-O { C55 Italian Game: Scotch Gambit } 5... Nxe4 6. Re1 d5 7. Bxd5 Qxd5 8. Nc3 { [%cal Gd1d5,Gc3e4,Ge1e4,Gf3d4] } 8... Qa5 9. Nxe4) (5. Ng5 { C55 Italian Game/Two Knights Defense/Perreux Variation } 5... d5 6. exd5 Qe7+ 7. Kf1 Ne5) (5. Nxd4 Nxe4) 5... d5 6. Bb5 Ne4 7. Nxd4 Bc5) (4. c3 { Goering Gambit } 4... dxc3 5. Bc4 { Goering Gambit/Double Pawn Sacrifice } (5. Nxc3 d6 6. Bc4 Nf6 7. Qb3 { [%cal Gb3f7] } 7... Qd7 8. Ng5 { [%cal Gb3f7,Gg5f7] } 8... Ne5) 5... cxb2 6. Bxb2) (4. Bb5 { Reifsson Gambit } 4... a6 (4... Bc5) 5. Bxc6 dxc6) 4... Bc5 { Classical Variation } (4... Nf6 { Schmidt Variation } 5. Nxc6 (5. Nc3 Bb4 6. Nxc6 bxc6 7. Bd3 d5 8. exd5 cxd5 9. O-O O-O 10. Bg5 c6 11. Qf3) 5... bxc6 6. e5 { Mieses Variation } 6... Qe7 7. Qe2 Nd5 8. c4 Ba6 9. b3) (4... Bb4+ { Malaniuk Variation } 5. c3 Bc5 6. Nxc6 bxc6 7. Bd3) (4... Qf6 5. Be3 Bc5 6. c3 Nge7 7. Bc4) (4... Nxd4?! 5. Qxd4 Qf6) 5. Be3 (5. Nb3 { Potter Variation } 5... Bb6 6. Nc3 Nf6) (5. Nf5 d5 6. Nxg7+ Kf8 7. Nh5 Qh4 8. Ng3 Nf6 9. Be2 dxe4) (5. c3 Nf6) (5. Nxc6 Qf6 { Classical Variation/Intermezzo Variation } { [%cal Rf6f2,Rc5f2] } (5... bxc6 6. Bd3 d6 (6... Qh4)) 6. Qd2 (6. Qf3 dxc6 7. Nc3 Be6) 6... dxc6 7. Nc3) 5... Bxd4 (5... Bb6 6. Nc3) (5... Qf6 6. c3 Nge7 7. Bc4 Ne5 8. Be2 Qg6 { [%cal Rg6g2,Rg6e4] } 9. O-O d6 (9... Qxe4?! 10. Nd2 Qg6 11. Bh5 Qd3 (11... Qb6? 12. b4) 12. Be2 Qg6 13. Bh5 Qd3) 10. f3 O-O) 6. Bxd4 Nf6 7. Nc3 *


