1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 exd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nxc6 bxc6 6. e5 { Mieses Variation } 6... Qe7 { is the only good move. } 7. Qe2 { the only good response. } 7... Nd5 8. c4 Ba6 (8... Nb6 9. Nc3 (9. g3) (9. Nd2) (9. b3) 9... Qe6 10. Qe4 (10. Bd2) 10... g6 11. Bd3 (11. f4) (11. Bd2) 11... Bg7 (11... Ba6) 12. f4 (12. O-O) 12... O-O 13. O-O Ba6 (13... f5 14. Qf3 { Best move. } { [%cal Gf3c6] } (14. Qe2 { Also playable. } 14... d6 15. c5 Nd5 16. Nxd5 cxd5 17. exd6 cxd6 18. Qxe6+ Bxe6 { Morelli, Angel - Peigney, Christophe, 1/2-1/2, LIPEAD40/sf G 16 (PER), 2014, https://lichess.org/bFVU8ZKk } 19. Re1) 14... Nxc4 15. Rd1 $10) (13... d6 14. Qxc6 dxe5 15. Qxc7 f5 16. c5 Rf7 17. Qd8+ Rf8 18. Qc7 { is a draw after } (18. Qh4 { keeps the game going. } 18... e4! 19. Bc2 Nc4 20. Bb3 Qf7) 18... Rf7) 14. b3 (14. c5) 14... f5 (14... d5?!) 15. Qe2 (15. Qf3) 15... d6 16. Ba3 Rfd8 { Bressac, S. - Gascon Del Nogal, Jose Rafael, 0-1, 6th Lorca Open 2017, https://lichess.org/8T3dnoI1 } (16... c5 { Pugh, John - Klausen, Tor-Arne, 1/2-1/2, EU/C2015/ct05, https://lichess.org/xnc4r9cm })) 9. b3 g6 (9... O-O-O 10. g3 (10. Bb2) 10... f6 (10... g5)) (9... Qh4) 10. f4 (10. g3 Bg7 11. Bb2 O-O 12. Bg2 Rae8 13. O-O Bxe5 { The following variations end all in the same position: } 14. Qxe5 (14. Bxe5 { Just a different move order. } 14... Qxe5 15. Qxe5 Rxe5 16. cxd5 Bxf1 17. Kxf1 cxd5 18. Nc3 c6) 14... Qxe5 15. Bxe5 Rxe5 16. cxd5 Bxf1 17. Kxf1 cxd5 18. Nc3 c6) (10. Bb2 Bg7 11. g3 O-O (11... O-O-O) 12. Bg2 (12. Bh3) 12... Rae8 { goes into the same line as the 10.g3 line above: } 13. O-O Bxe5 14. Qxe5 Qxe5 15. Bxe5 Rxe5 16. cxd5 Bxf1 17. Kxf1 cxd5 18. Nc3 c6) 10... d6 11. Qf2 (11. Bb2) (11. Qd2) 11... Nf6 (11... Nb6) 12. Be2 (12. Ba3) 12... dxe5 13. O-O (13. Ba3) (13. Nc3) 13... Ne4 14. Qe1 O-O-O (14... Qc5+) 15. Nc3 Nc5 16. fxe5 Bg7 17. Na4 (17. Bf4) 17... Nxa4 18. Bg4+ Kb7 (18... Kb8) 19. bxa4 Qxe5 20. Rb1+ Ka8 21. Bf3 Qc5+ 22. Kh1 (22. Be3?!) 22... Rhe8 (22... Bb7) 23. Qh4 Rd6 24. Bf4 Rde6 25. Rfd1 (25. Bg3) (25. h3) 25... Bf6 26. Qg3 Bd4 (26... h5) (26... Bxc4) *


