1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 cxd5 4. c4 Nf6 5. Nc3 Nc6 { Panov Attack/Modern Defense. } 6. Nf3 (6. Bg5 e6 { Carlsbad Line } (6... Qa5 { Czerniak Line }) (6... Qb6 { Reifir-Spielmann Line }) (6... Be6) (6... dxc4)) (6. cxd5) 6... Bg4 { Mieses Line } 7. cxd5 Nxd5 8. Qb3 Bxf3 9. gxf3 e6 10. Qxb7 Nxd4 11. Bb5+ Nxb5 12. Qc6+ { is as good as the immediate Qxb5. } (12. Qxb5+ Qd7 13. Qxd7+ (13. Nxd5 { Sneaky trap, if Black dares to take White's queen first. } 13... exd5 (13... Qxb5?? 14. Nc7+ Kd7 15. Nxb5 $18) 14. Qxd7+ Kxd7) 13... Kxd7 14. Nxd5 exd5 { █ █ █ █ █ }) 12... Ke7 13. Qxb5 Qd7 14. Nxd5+ Qxd5 15. Qxd5 exd5 *


