1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 g6 6. Be3 Bg7 7. f3 O-O 8. Qd2 Nc6 9. Bc4 Bd7 10. O-O-O Rc8 { Called "Old Line", but it is still the main line. Black will try to open the c-file (Rxc3! is thematic), and White will attack Black's kingside after exchanging Black dark-squared bishop. } { [%csl Bc3,Bc2][%cal Rc8c3,Gh2h5,Gg2g5,Ge3h6,Gh6g7,Rd7e6,Re6a2] } 11. Bb3 { Step out of the rook's view. } { [%csl Rc4][%cal Rc8c4] } (11. Be2 a6) 11... Ne5 { [%cal Rc8c3] } (11... Nxd4 12. Bxd4 b5 { [%cal Gb5b4] } 13. Nd5 Nxd5 14. Bxg7 Kxg7 15. exd5 (15. Bxd5 a5)) 12. Kb1 Re8 (12... a6 13. h4 (13. Rhe1 { An interesting sideline with a few twists: } 13... b5 14. Bh6 Bxh6 15. Qxh6 Rxc3!? 16. bxc3 a5 17. f4 Neg4 18. Qh4 a4 19. Bxf7+!? Rxf7 20. e5 Nd5 21. e6 Nxc3+ 22. Kc1 Bxe6 23. Nxe6 Qa5 24. Qxg4 Nxa2+ 25. Kb2 Qc3+ 26. Kxa2 Qxc2+ 27. Ka1 Qc3+ 28. Kb1 Qb3+ 29. Ka1 Qc3+ { Ivanchuk, Vassily - Carlsen, Magnus, 1/2-1/2, Grand Slam Final 1st, 2008, https://lichess.org/oW0O0nCK }) (13. Bh6 Bxh6 14. Qxh6 Rxc3 15. bxc3 a5) (13. g4 b5) 13... h5 14. Bh6 (14. g4 hxg4 15. h5 Nxh5 16. Rdg1 (16. Bh6 e6 17. Rdg1 Qf6 18. fxg4 Bxh6 19. Qxh6 Qg7 20. Qe3 Nf6 21. g5 Nh5 22. Nde2 a5 23. Rxh5 gxh5 24. Nf4 Ng4 25. Qh3 Qd4 26. Nce2 Qxe4 27. Qxh5 a4 28. Rh1 Qxh1+ 29. Qxh1 axb3 30. axb3 Bc6 31. Qh4 Be4 32. Nc3 Bf5 33. Nh5 f6 34. Ng3 Rc7 35. Nxf5 exf5 36. gxf6 Nxf6 37. Qg5+ Kf7 38. Qxf5 Re7 39. b4 Re5 40. Qf2 Rd8 41. b3 Rd7 42. Kb2 Rde7 43. Qb6 Rd7 44. Qd4 Ke7 45. Qd3 Kf7 46. Nb5 Ke7 47. Nd4 Kf7 48. Qf3 Rh5 49. Nf5 Ke6 50. Nd4+ Kf7 51. Nf5 Ke6 52. Nd4+ { Dominguez Perez, Leinier - Carlsen, Magnus, 1/2-1/2, Biel GM 41st, 2008, https://lichess.org/ubhANS4Z }) 16... Qa5 (16... Rc5 17. Bh6 Kh7 18. Bxg7 Kxg7 19. f4 Nc4 20. Bxc4 Rxc4 21. f5 e5 22. Nde2 Rh8 23. b3 Rc6 24. Rxg4 Nf6 25. Rgg1 Rxh1 26. Rxh1 Ng4 27. Ng3 Kg8 28. Nd5 Rc5 29. Ne3 Nxe3 30. Qxe3 Qf6 31. Qh6 Qg7 32. Qg5 f6 33. Qd2 Rc6 34. Kb2 gxf5 35. Qa5 Qe7 36. Qd5+ Be6 37. Qd1 Qg7 38. exf5 Bf7 39. Ne4 Kf8 40. Nxd6 Ke7 41. Nxb7 Qg8 42. Qd2 Rb6 43. Rd1 Qc8 44. Nd6 Qd7 45. Nxf7 Qxd2 46. Rxd2 Kxf7 47. c4 Ke7 48. Kc3 { Topalov, Veselin - Carlsen, Magnus, 1-0, Grand Slam Final 1st, 2008, https://lichess.org/wfuJE4T3 }) 17. Bh6 Rxc3 18. Bxg7 Kxg7 19. Rxh5 Rxb3 20. Qxa5 Rxb2+ 21. Ka1 gxh5 22. f4 Be6 23. Nxe6+ fxe6 24. fxe5 Rb5 25. Qc7 Rxe5 26. Qxe7+ Rf7 27. Qxd6 Rxe4 28. Rh1 Rf5 29. Qe7+ Kg6 30. Qe8+ Kg7 31. Rd1 Rd5 32. Rxd5 exd5 33. Qxh5 b5 34. Qg5+ Kh7 35. Qxd5 Ra4 36. Qg5 Rc4 37. Kb2 Rb4+ 38. Kc1 Ra4 39. a3 Rc4 40. Kd2 Rd4+ 41. Ke1 Ra4 42. Kf1 Rc4 43. Kg1 Rc6 44. Qd5 Rg6 45. a4 bxa4 46. Qd7+ Kh6 47. Qxa4 Kg5 48. c4 Kf5 49. c5 Ke5 50. Qd7 { Anand, Viswanathan - Carlsen, Magnus, 1-0, Mainz Classic rap fin, 2008, https://lichess.org/cvKvhZx8 }) 14... Nc4 15. Bxc4 Rxc4 16. Bxg7 Kxg7 17. Rhe1 Re8 18. Nde2 Qa5 19. Nf4 Rec8 20. Ncd5 Qxd2 21. Rxd2 Nxd5 22. Nxd5 Re8 23. Nb6 Rc7 24. e5 Be6 25. exd6 Rc6 26. Na4 exd6 27. b3 Rec8 28. Nb2 Rc5 29. Ree2 Re5 30. Nd3 Rxe2 31. Rxe2 { Anand, Viswanathan - Carlsen, Magnus, 1/2-1/2, Mainz Classic rap Prelim, 2008, https://lichess.org/w3yzPrTD }) 13. h4 h5 14. Bh6 Nc4 15. Bxc4 Rxc4 16. Bxg7 Kxg7 17. Nd5 e5 18. Nxf6 Qxf6 19. Nb3 Rec8 20. Qxd6 Be6 21. c3 b5 (21... R4c6) 22. Qd2 a5 23. Qg5 Qxg5 24. hxg5 a4 25. Nd2 R4c7 26. a3 Rd7 27. Kc1 f6 28. gxf6+ Kxf6 29. Nf1 Rxd1+ 30. Kxd1 Rd8+ 31. Ke1 Kg5 32. g3 Rd3 33. Nd2 Bc4 34. Nxc4 bxc4 35. Ke2 Rd6 36. Rh2 { Leko, Peter - Carlsen, Magnus, 1/2-1/2, Miskolc m, 2008, https://lichess.org/b5RQMwtm } 1/2 - 1/2


