1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. c3 d5 4. Qa4 Nf6?! { Leonhardt Variation } 5. Nxe5 { White has to take the pawn. } 5... Nxe4 (5... Bd6 { Main move according to lichess' database. } 6. Nxc6 bxc6 7. d3 O-O 8. Nd2 (8. Be2)) 6. Nxc6 { [%cal Gc6d8] } (6. Bb5 Qf6 { [%cal Rf6c6,Rf6e5,Rf6f2,Re4f2] } 7. O-O Qxe5 (7... Nc5) 8. Bxc6+ Kd8 9. d4 Qh5 10. Bf4 Qf5 11. Be5 f6 12. Bxd5 fxe5 13. dxe5 Nc5 14. Qd4 $15) 6... Qd7 (6... bxc6?! 7. Qxc6+ { [%cal Gc6a8,Gc6e8] } 7... Bd7 8. Qxd5 Nf6 { [%cal Rf6d5] } 9. Qd4 Bd6 10. Bc4 O-O 11. O-O Ng4 { [%cal Rd6h2,Rg4h2] } 12. g3 Qg5 { [%cal Rg5h5,Rh5h2,Rg4h2] } 13. Qd5 Qg6 14. Qg2 Ne5 { [%cal Re5c4] } 15. Bd5 { [%cal Gd5a8] } 15... c6 16. Be4 Qh5 { [%cal Rd7h3] } 17. h4 f5 18. d4 fxe4 19. dxe5 Bxe5 $10) 7. d4 (7. Bb5?! Nc5) 7... bxc6 8. Nd2 Bd6 $10 *


