1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 { C42 Russian Game/General } 3. Nxe5 (3. d4 { ➡ Modern Attack } 3... Nxe4 (3... exd4 4. e5 (4. Bc4 { Modern Attack/Suchting Gambit = Bishop's Opening/Urusov Gambit }) 4... Ne4 5. Bb5 { Modern Attack/Tal Gambit } (5. Qxd4 { Modern Attack/Center Attack })) (3... d5 { Modern Attack/Symmetrical Variation }) 4. Bd3 { Modern Attack/Center Variation } 4... Nc6 { Modern Attack/Murrey Variation } (4... d5 5. Nxe5 Bd6 6. O-O O-O 7. c4 Bxe5 { Modern Attack/Trifunovic Variation })) (3. Qe2 Nc6 4. d4 { Moody Gambit }) (3. Nc3 { chessestense }) (3. Bc4 { Urusov Gambit }) (3. d3 Nc6 4. g3 { King's Indian Attack. That's not the official name, but the system White is playing here. }) (3. Bd3? d5 4. Qe2 (4. exd5 e4 5. Qe2 Qe7 6. d6 (6. Bb5+ c6 7. d6 Qxd6 8. Bc4 Be6 9. Ng5 Bxc4 10. Qxc4 Qd5 $15) 6... cxd6 7. Bb5+ Bd7 8. Bxd7+ Nbxd7 9. Nd4 Qe5 $15) 4... dxe4 5. Bxe4 Nxe4 6. Qxe4 Nc6 7. O-O f5) 3... d6 (3... Nxe4 { Damiano Variation } 4. Qe2 Qe7 { Damiano Variation/Kholmov Gambit }) (3... Nc6 { Stafford Gambit }) (3... Qe7 4. d4 d6 5. Nf3 Qxe4+ (5... Nxe4 6. Be2 d5) 6. Be2 Bf5 { [%cal Re4c2] }) 4. Nf3 (4. Nxf7 { ➡ Cochrane Gambit } 4... Kxf7 5. Bc4+ { Cochrane Gambit/Bishop check line } (5. d4 { Cochrane Gambit/Center Variation })) (4. Nd3 { Karklins-Martinovsky Variation }) (4. Nc4 { Paulsen Attack }) 4... Nxe4 5. d4 { Classical Attack } (5. Qe2 { Cozio (Lasker) Attack }) (5. d3 { French Attack }) (5. c4 { Kaufmann Attack }) (5. Bd3 { Millenium Attack }) (5. Nc3 { Nimzowitsch Attack }) 5... d5 (5... Nf6 { Classical Attack/Closed Variation }) (5... Be7 6. Bd3 d5 7. O-O) 6. Bd3 Be7 (6... Bd6 { Classical Attack/Marshall Variation } 7. O-O O-O 8. c4 c6 { Classical Attack/Staunton Variation } (8... Bg4 { Classical Attack/Tarrasch Variation }) 9. Re1 Bg4 { Classical Attack/Marshall Variation/Chinese Gambit }) (6... Nc6 { Classical Attack/Mason-Showalter Variation }) (6... Bb4+ 7. c3 Be7) (6... Nd6 7. O-O Be7 8. Bf4 O-O) 7. O-O Nc6 (7... O-O { Classical Attack/Mason Variation }) 8. c4 { Classical Attack/Jaenisch Variation } (8. Re1 { Classical Attack/Chigorin Variation } 8... Bg4 9. c3 f5 10. Nbd2 { Classical Attack/Berger Variation }) 8... Nb4 9. cxd5 { Classical Attack/Chigorin Variation/Browne Attack } (9. Be2 { Classical Attack/Chigorin Variation/Main Line }) *


