1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nxe5 d6 4. Nxf7 { Cochrane Gambit } 4... Kxf7 5. Nc3 { Threat is Bc4+ } { [%cal Gc3e4,Bf1c4] } (5. d4 { is the main move }) 5... c5 (5... Be6 { is probably the best move here. } 6. d4 Kg8 7. f4 Nbd7 8. Be2 c5 9. Be3 $15 { Krzyzanowski, Antoni - Jørgensen, Poul Erik, 1/2-1/2, WS/M/282, 2010, https://lichess.org/zwT6osAI }) 6. Bc4+ Be6 7. Bxe6+ { The idea is to keep Black's king in the center. } 7... Kxe6 8. d4 Kf7 (8... cxd4?! 9. Qxd4 Kf7 10. Qc4+ d5 11. Nxd5 Nxd5 12. O-O $10 (12. exd5? Qe7+! { [%cal Re7b4,Bb4e1,Bb4c4] })) 9. dxc5 { [%cal Gd1d8] } 9... Nc6 (9... Qc7 10. Be3) 10. Qe2 Qd7 11. Be3 dxc5 12. f4 Re8 13. e5 Ng4 14. Rd1 Qf5 15. O-O h5 16. Bc1 Nd4 17. Qc4+ Kg6 18. h3 Nh6 19. Nb5 a6 20. Nxd4 cxd4 21. Qxd4 Rc8 22. Qb6+ Kh7 23. Qxb7 Rxc2 24. Be3 Qg6 25. Rc1 Rxc1 26. Rxc1 Nf5 27. Bf2 h4 28. Rc7 Ng3 29. Kh2 Nf1+ 30. Kg1 Qb1 31. Bxh4 Bc5+ { 1/2-1/2 The game is a draw. } 1/2-1/2


