1. d4 (1. g3 d5 2. Bg2 e6 { Hungarian Opening/Catalan Formation. Note that e6 is a rather rare move here. If you want a Catalan, don't start with g3. } (2... Nf6 { Main move besides c6. })) (1. c4 e6 2. Nf3 d5 3. g3 Nf6 { A14 English Opening/Agincourt Defense/Neo-Catalan } 4. Bg2 Be7 (4... dxc4 { Catalan Defense Accepted }) (4... c6 { The full name deserves to be written out: English Opening/Agincourt Defense/Catalan Defense/Semi-Slav Defense }) (4... Bd6 { Bogoljubow Defense. Technically not a Catalan anymore. }) (4... c5 5. O-O Nc6 6. cxd5 exd5 (6... Nxd5 7. d4 (7. Nc3 Be7 { Agincourt Defense/Keres Defense } 8. d4 O-O 9. e4)) 7. d4 Be7 8. Nc3 (8. dxc5 Bxc5 9. Bg5 O-O 10. Nc3 d4 11. Bxf6 Qxf6 12. Nd5 (12. Ne4)) 8... O-O { Transposition: D34 Tarrasch Defense: Classical Variation }) 5. O-O { Neo-Catalan Declined }) 1... Nf6 (1... d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. g3 { Queen's Pawn Game/Symmetrical Variation/Pseudo-Catalan }) 2. c4 e6 3. g3 { E00 Catalan Opening } 3... d5 (3... e5 { Hungarian Gambit }) 4. Bg2 { E01 Closed Variation } 4... Be7 (4... dxc4 5. Qa4+ { E02 Open Defense } (5. Nf3 { E04 Open Defense } 5... Be7 { Open Defense/Classical Line } (5... Nc6 6. Qa4 Bb4+ { Open Defense/Modern Sharp Variation }) (5... a6 6. O-O Nc6 (6... b5 7. Ne5 Nd5 8. a4 (8. Nc3 Bb7 9. Nxd5 exd5 10. e4 dxe4 11. Qh5 g6 12. Nxg6 fxg6 13. Qe5+ Qe7 14. Qxh8 Nd7) 8... Bb7) 7. e3 Bd7 (7... Rb8) (7... Nd7))) 5... Nbd7 6. Qxc4 a6 7. Qc2 { Open Defense/Alekhine Variation }) (4... c5 5. Nf3 (5. cxd5 exd5 (5... Nxd5) (5... cxd4)) 5... Nc6 { Open Defense/Tarrasch Defense }) (4... Bb4+ 5. Bd2 Be7 { The idea of this maneuver is it to misplace White's dark-squared bishop that would be better placed on b2 later. } 6. Nf3 O-O 7. O-O c6 8. Qc2 b6 (8... Nbd7 9. Bf4 b6) 9. Ne5 (9. Bf4) (9. Rd1)) 5. Nf3 { E06 Closed Variation } 5... O-O 6. O-O dxc4 (6... c6) (6... b6) (6... Nbd7 { E07 Closed Variation } 7. Qc2 { E08 Closed Variation } (7. Nc3 c6 (7... dxc4) 8. Qd3 { Botvinnik Variation } (8. b3 b6)) 7... c6 8. Nbd2 (8. b3 b6 9. Rd1 Bb7 10. Nc3 Rc8 11. e4 dxe4 12. Nxe4 (12. Ng5 h6 13. Ngxe4 Nxe4 14. Nxe4 Nf6)) (8. Rd1) 8... b6 { Traditional Variation } (8... b5 { Rabinovich Variation })) 7. Qc2 (7. Ne5 Nc6 8. Nxc6 (8. Bxc6 bxc6 9. Nxc6 Qe8 10. Nxe7+ Qxe7 11. Qa4 e5 12. dxe5 Qxe5 13. Qxc4 Be6) 8... bxc6 9. Na3 Bxa3 10. bxa3) 7... a6 8. a4 (8. Qxc4 b5 9. Qc2 Bb7 10. Bd2 Be4 11. Qc1 Bb7 (11... c6)) 8... Bd7 9. Qxc4 Bc6 10. Bg5 (10. Bf4 a5 (10... Bd6) (10... Nbd7 11. Nc3)) 10... Bd5 (10... a5 11. Nc3 Na6) (10... Nbd7 11. Nc3) 11. Qd3 (11. Qc2 Be4 12. Qc1 h6) 11... c5 (11... Be4 12. Qe3 Nbd7 13. Nc3 Bc6 14. Qd3) 12. Nc3 (12. dxc5) 12... Bc6 (12... cxd4 13. Nxd5) 13. Rfd1 cxd4 (13... Qa5) 14. Nxd4 Bxg2 15. Kxg2 Nbd7 *


