1. Nf3 (1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nf3 Bg7 4. g3 b6 5. Bg2 Bb7 { Alternative route to the position after move 5. }) 1... Nf6 2. c4 { [%csl Gd5,Ge5,Re4][%cal Gc4d5,Gf3e5,Rf6e4] } 2... b6 { A15 English Opening: Anglo-Indian Defense, Queen's Indian Formation } { [%csl Rc5,Re4,Gd5,Ge5][%cal Rb6c5,Rf6e4,Gc4d5,Gf3e5] } 3. g3 Bb7 4. Bg2 g6 5. d4 Bg7 { The key position for this chapter.
This position can also be reached via 1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 g6 3.Nf3 Bg7 4.g3 b6 Bb7. } 6. O-O O-O 7. d5 Na6 (7... e6 8. Nc3 exd5 9. cxd5 Re8 10. Nd4 Na6 11. Bf4 Nc5 12. Qc2?! (12. Ndb5! { prevents the rook sacrifice } 12... d6 13. b4) 12... Nh5 13. Be3 Rxe3!? { Playable, but not very sound. } 14. fxe3 Qg5?! (14... Qe7 15. Qd2 { Black's compensation is the bishop pair and White's poor pawn structure. }) 15. Qd2 Re8 16. Nf3?! { Sadhwani, Raunak - Donchenko, Alexander, 6th Purtichju Open 2019, 0-1 } (16. Ndb5! $146)) 8. Nc3 Nc5 9. Nd4 { Enabling f2-f4. } { [%cal Gf2f4] } *


