+ { [%eval 0.8] } 22... Kg8 { [%eval 0.91] } 23. Rxd6 { [%eval 0.61] } (23. N3d2! { [%cal Gd2e4,Gd2c4] } 23... Qc2 24. Qxc2 Bxc2 25. Bxa8 Bxd1 26. Rxd1 Rxa8 27. Ne3 Re8 28. Ndc4 $14 { [%cal Gc4d6,Gc4b6,Gd1d6] }) 23... Qc5?! { [%eval 1.48] } { Inaccuracy. Best move was Qc7. } (23... Qc7 24. Rad1) 24. Rad1 { [%eval 1.17] } 24... Ra7?! { [%eval 1.88] } { Inaccuracy. Best move was Rac8. } (24... Rac8 25. Ne3) 25. Ne3 { [%eval 1.71] } 25... Qh5? { [%eval 3.29] } { Mistake. Best move was h5. } (25... h5 26. h4) 26. Nd4? { [%eval 1.58] } { Mistake. } (26. R1d5! { Not so easy to find. } 26... Bxd5 27. g4 { The queen is trapped. } 27... Qh3 28. Bxh3 Bxf3 29. Bg2 $18) 26... Bxg2 { [%eval 1.31] } 27. Kxg2 { [%eval 1.57] } 27... Qe5?! { [%eval 2.65] } { Inaccuracy. Best move was Rxe3. } (27... Rxe3 28. fxe3 Ne5 29. Qe2 Qxe2+ 30. Nxe2 Nc4 { [%cal Gc4e3,Gc4d6] } 31. Kf3 Nxd6 32. Rxd6 Rb7 33. Nc3 Kg7 34. Rc6) 28. Nc4 { [%eval 2.55] } 28... Qc5 { [%eval 2.88] } 29. Nc6 { [%eval 2.82] } 29... Rc7 { [%eval 3.03] } 30. Ne3?! { [%eval 2.33] } { Inaccuracy. Best move was R1d4. } (30. R1d4) 30... Ne5?? { [%eval 5.67] } { Blunder. Best move was Rxe3. } (30... Rxe3 31. fxe3 Qxe3) 31. R1d5 { [%eval 4.48] } { 1-0 Black resigns. } 1-0


