1. e4 e5 2. b3 Nf6 3. Bb2 Nc6 { Two Knights Defense. Black keeps the center closed and just defends e5. } 4. Nf3 { [%cal Gb2e5,Gf3e5] } 4... Bc5 { [%cal Rc5f2,Rf6g4,Rg4f2,Rf6e4,Re4f2] } (4... Nxe4 5. d3 Nf6 (5... Ng5) 6. Nxe5 Nxe5 7. Bxe5 d5) 5. Nc3 { [%cal Gc3e4] } 5... O-O (5... Ng4 6. d4! { The only move. } 6... exd4 7. Nd5 O-O (7... d3?! 8. Qxd3 { This looks like f2 is falling, but that pawn is poisoned. White has excellent counterplay. } { [%cal Rg4f2,Rc5f2] } 8... Nb4 { [%cal Rb4d3] } (8... Bxf2+?! 9. Ke2 Bc5 10. Qc3 { [%cal Gc3c5,Gc3g7] } 10... Bf8 11. h3 Nf6 { [%cal Gf6e4] } 12. Re1 { [%cal Ge1e8] } 12... Be7 13. Kd2 { [%cal Ge1e4] }) (8... Nxf2? { [%cal Rf2h1,Rf2d3] } 9. Qc3 { [%cal Gc3c5,Gc3g7] } 9... Rg8 (9... Nxe4? 10. Qxg7 Bf2+ $18 { FM Sergey_Naboka - volitionwill, 1-0, -, https://lichess.org/XwBmVpgr } 11. Ke2 Rf8 12. Qxh7 { [%cal Gh7e4] }) 10. Qxc5 Nxh1 11. O-O-O $16 { And the knight is trapped. } { [%csl Bh1,Gf2,Gg3][%cal Gc5f2,Gh2g3] }) 9. Nxb4 Bxb4+ 10. Nd2 Qg5 { [%cal Rb4d2,Rg5d2] } 11. f3 Qe3+ 12. Qxe3 Nxe3 13. Ke2 $14)) 6. Bd3 a6 7. O-O { Finally securing f2. } 7... d6 8. h3 (8. Re1) *


