1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 a6 6. Be3 { B90 English Attack. This has become the modern main line. Since the early 1990s, the English Attack, 6. Be3 followed by f3, g4, Qd2 and 0-0-0 in some order, has become extremely popular. } { [%cal Gf2f3,Gg2g4,Gd1d2,Ge1c1] } 6... e5 (6... e6 { Black tries to transpose to the Scheveningen. f3 will keep the game in the English Attack, g4 goes into the Scheveningen/Keres attack. } 7. f3 (7. g4 e5 8. Nf5 g6 9. g5 gxf5 10. exf5 (10. gxf6 f4 11. Bd2 Nd7 12. Bc4 Nxf6 13. Rg1 $15) 10... d5 11. Qf3 d4 12. O-O-O Nbd7 13. Bc4 Qc7 14. Bxd4 exd4 15. Rhe1+ Kd8 16. Rxd4 Bc5 17. Rdd1 Re8 18. gxf6 Rxe1 19. Rxe1 Nxf6 20. Rd1+) 7... b5 8. Qd2 (8. g4 h6 9. Qd2 b4 (9... Nbd7 10. O-O-O Bb7 11. h4 b4 12. Na4 Qa5 13. b3 Nc5 14. a3 Nxa4 15. axb4 Qc7 16. bxa4 d5 17. e5 Nd7 18. f4 Nb6 19. Rh3 Nxa4 20. Bf2 Be7 21. f5 Rc8 22. Be1 exf5 23. gxf5 Qxe5 24. Ra3 Nb6 25. Bg3 Qf6 $10) 10. Nce2 (10. Na4 Nbd7 11. O-O-O Ne5 12. Qxb4 Bd7 13. Bf4 g5 14. Bd2 Rb8 15. Qa3 Be7 $10) 10... e5 11. Nb3 (11. Nf5 d5 12. O-O-O Be6 13. Kb1 Nc6 14. Nc1 d4 15. Bf2 g6 16. Ng3) 11... a5 (11... Nc6) (11... Be6) 12. a3 (12. a4) (12. Ng3 a4 13. Nc1 (13. Bb5+) 13... d5 14. Bb5+ (14. Nd3) (14. exd5) 14... Bd7 15. Bxd7+ Qxd7 (15... Nbxd7) 16. exd5 Nxd5 17. Nd3 (17. O-O) 17... a3 18. b3 Nc6 (18... f6 19. f4 Nc6 (19... exf4) 20. fxe5 fxe5 $10) (18... Qe6 19. O-O-O (19. O-O Nc6) 19... Nc6 20. Nc5 Bxc5 21. Bxc5) 19. Nc5 (19. O-O Rd8 20. Rae1 { [%cal Gd3f4,Ge3f4] } 20... Nxe3 (20... f6) 21. Qxe3 { [%cal Gd3e5,Ge3e5,Be1e5,Rc6e5,Rd7e5] } 21... Bd6 22. Nf5 { [%cal Gf5d6,Gf5g7] } 22... O-O $10) 19... Bxc5 20. Bxc5 O-O-O $10)) 8... Nbd7 9. g4) (6... Ng4 { Anti-English } 7. Bg5 (7. Bc1 Nf6 8. Be3 (8. Bg5) (8. Be2) 8... e5 (8... e6 9. f3 (9. g4) (9. Be2) 9... b5 10. Qd2 Nbd7 11. g4 h6 (11... b4 12. Nce2 h6 13. O-O-O Qc7 14. h4 d5 15. Bf4 e5 16. Bh2 dxe4 17. g5 hxg5 18. hxg5 Rxh2 19. Rxh2 exd4 20. Rh8 Nd5 21. Qxd4 Bb7 22. fxe4 N5b6 23. Qxb4 O-O-O 24. Qd4 Qc5 25. e5 Qxd4 (25... Be7 2