1. c4 c5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Nc3 d5 4. cxd5 Nxd5 5. e4 Nb4 6. Bc4 { This is not the best move, but still the main line. The bishop cannot be attacked here so easily, and it seems to put pressure on f7. In the following games we will see why both assumptions are wrong. } { [%csl Gf7][%cal Gc4f7] } 6... Nd3+ *


