1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Nf6 4. Ng5 { [%cal Rg5f7,Rc4f7] } 4... Bc5 { The Traxler Counterattack. This might work against someone completely unprepared. It's pretty bad otherwise. } { [%cal Gc5f2,Rg5f7,Rc4f7] } (4... d5 5. exd5 Na5 { → Polerio Defense } (5... Nxd5 { → Fried Liver Attack })) 5. Nxf7 { "Knight Sacrifice Line" } (5. Bxf7+ { "Bishop Sacrifice Line" } 5... Ke7 6. Bd5 (6. Bb3 Rf8 7. O-O d6 8. Nc3 Qe8 9. Nd5+ Kd8) (6. Bc4 Rf8 (6... Qe8 { [%cal Ge8g6,Gg6g2,Gg6e4] } 7. d3) 7. O-O) 6... Rf8 7. O-O d6 8. c3 Bg4 9. Nf3 Qe8) 5... Bxf2+ { It is important for White NOT to take this bishop. } 6. Kf1! (6. Kxf2?! Nxe4+ 7. Kg1 Qh4 { [%cal Gh4f2,Ge4f2] } 8. g3 Nxg3 9. Nxh8 (9. hxg3 Qxg3+ 10. Kf1 Rf8 11. Qh5 d5 12. Bxd5 Nb4 13. Qh2 Qxh2 14. Rxh2 Nxd5) 9... d5 10. Qe1 { [%cal Ge1e5] } 10... Qd4+ 11. Qe3 Nxh1 12. Bb5 Qg4+ 13. Kxh1 Be6 14. Qxe5 O-O-O { [%cal Gd8h8] } 15. Qe2 Qh3 16. Qe3) 6... Qe7 7. Nxh8 d5 8. exd5 Nd4 9. d6 { [%csl Gf7][%cal Gc4f7,Gh8f7,Gd6e7] } 9... Qxd6 (9... cxd6?! 10. Kxf2 Bg4 { [%cal Gg4d1] } 11. Qf1 Nxc2 12. h3 Be6 13. Bxe6 Qxe6 14. Qb5+ Qd7 (14... Kf8 15. Qxb7 { [%cal Gb7a8] } 15... Re8 16. d3 Nxa1 17. Na3) 15. Na3 Nxa1 16. d4) 10. c3 (10. Nf7? Qc5 (10... Qe7) 11. d3) 10... Bg4 11. Qa4+ Nd7 12. Kxf2 Qf6+ 13. Ke1 O-O-O (13... Qh4+ 14. g3 Nf3+ 15. Kf2 Qf6 16. Rf1 Nxh2+ 17. Kg2 Qh6 18. Kf2 Qf6+ 19. Kg2 Qh6 20. Qb4 Qh3+ 21. Kf2 (21. Kg1?? Qxg3+ 22. Kh1 Nxf1 23. Bf7+ Kd8 24. Qe7+ Kxe7 25. Ng6+ hxg6 26. a3 Bf3#) 21... O-O-O 22. Nf7 Bf3 23. Rg1 (23. Nxd8?? Qg2+ 24. Ke1 Qxg3+ 25. Rf2 Ng4 26. Qxb7+ Bxb7 27. Nxb7 Nxf2)) 14. Nf7 Nb6 15. cxd4 Nxa4 16. Nxd8 Qh4+ *


