. Best move was Be1. } (34. Be1 R4d2 35. Bxd2 exd2 36. Kg2 Re1 37. Rxd2 Bxd2 38. Nxd2 Re2+ 39. Kg3 Rxd2 40. Kf4 fxg4 41. fxg4 Rxa2) 34... Rd5?? { (-7.26 → -4.20) Blunder. Best move was Rc1. } (34... Rc1 35. Be1 Rdd1 36. Nxe3 Rxe1+ 37. Rxe1 Rxe1+ 38. Nf1 Be3+ 39. Kg2 Re2+ 40. Kh1 Bxc5 41. Ng3 Rxa2 42. Nxf5) 35. Bb4? { (-4.20 → -6.93) Mistake. Best move was Be1. } (35. Be1 Rc1 36. Nxe3 Re5 37. b4 Bxe3+ 38. Kf1 fxg4 39. fxg4 Kf7 40. a3 Re6 41. a4 Ra1 42. a5 Rc1) 35... a5? { (-6.93 → -4.82) Mistake. Best move was Rc1. } (35... Rc1 36. Be1 Rdd1 37. Nxe3 Rxe1+ 38. Rxe1 Rxe1+ 39. Nf1 Be3+ 40. Kg2 Re2+ 41. Kh1 Bxc5 42. Ng3 Rxa2 43. Nxf5) 36. Bxa5 Rxc5 37. Bb6 Rcc1 38. Bxe3 Rxf1+?! { (-5.87 → -4.98) Inaccuracy. Best move was Bxe3+. } (38... Bxe3+ 39. Rxe3 f4 40. Re4 Rxf1+ 41. Kg2 Rfd1 42. Re2 Rg1+ 43. Kh2 Rg3 44. Rf2 Rc3 45. g5 Rxg5 46. h4) 39. Kg2 Bxe3 40. Rxe3 Rfe1? { (-6.18 → -4.82) Mistake. Best move was f4. } (40... f4 41. Re8+ Kf7 42. Re4 g5 43. b4 Rfd1 44. Re2 Rg1+ 45. Kh2 Rg3 46. Rb2 Rxf3 47. h4 Rcc3 48. hxg5) 41. Rd3? { (-4.82 → -7.01) Mistake. Best move was Kf2. } (41. Kf2 Rxe3 42. Kxe3 Rc3+ 43. Kf4 Kf7 44. Kxf5 Rxf3+ 45. Ke5 Rxh3 46. Kd6 Rd3+ 47. Kc5 Rc3+ 48. Kd6 Rg3) 41... f4?! { Black wins. } { (-7.01 → -6.13) Inaccuracy. Best move was Rc2+. } (41... Rc2+ 42. Kg3 g5 43. f4 Rg1+ 44. Kf3 Rf1+ 45. Kg3 gxf4+ 46. Kh4 Rxa2 47. Kg5 fxg4 48. hxg4 f3 49. Kf6) 0-1


