{ Since 2015, Ivan Cheparinov - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivan_Cheparinov - is playing the Dutch regularly. He has now become one of the leading experts in this opening, and I think his games are very creative, accurate and overall inspiring. Hence this study. }
1. d4 { I have also included his early games against the Dutch and his first unsuccessful attempt against Bogner from 2011, because this might help to follow the learning process he went through. } 1... f5 { My plan is to annotate every game … and to keep this study updated. } *


