1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Nf6 { C46 Four Knights Game } 4. d4 { C47 Scotch Variation } 4... exd4 { C47 Accepted } (4... Bb4 5. Nxe5 { C47 Krause Gambit } (5. d5 Nd4 { C47 Oxford Gambit }) 5... Qe7 { C47 Krause Gambit/Leonhardt Defense }) 5. Nxd4 (5. Nd5 { C47 Belgrade Gambit } 5... Nxe4 6. Qe2 f5 { C47 Belgrade Gambit/Modern Defense }) 5... Bb4 (5... Nxe4 { C47 Schmid Defense }) (5... Nxd4?! 6. Qxd4 d6 7. Bg5 Be7 8. O-O-O O-O 9. e5 Nd5 10. Bxe7 Nxe7 11. Qe4) 6. Nxc6 bxc6 { [%csl Ge4] } 7. Bd3 (7. Qd4 Qe7 8. f3 c5 9. Qe3 O-O $10 { White's queen moves gave black a head in development. }) 7... d5 (7... O-O 8. O-O d5 9. exd5 cxd5 10. Bg5 c6 11. Qf3 Bd6 (11... Be7) (11... Rb8)) 8. exd5 cxd5 9. O-O O-O 10. Bg5 c6 11. Qf3 Bd6 12. Rfe1 Rb8 13. Rab1 h6 14. Bxf6 Qxf6 15. Qxf6 gxf6 16. Ne2 c5 17. b3 Be6 18. Ng3 { [%cal Gg3h5,Gg3f5] } 18... c4 19. Bf5 Bxg3 20. Bxe6 fxe6 21. hxg3 cxb3 22. axb3 e5 23. Ra1 Rbc8 $10 *


[Event "3 and 4 knights opening: Theory, gambits, and important games: 4K/Scotch/Krause Gambit: 4…Bb4 5.Nxe5"]
[Date "2017.08.28"]
