1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. d4 exd4 5. Nd5 { Belgrade Gambit } { [%cal Gf3d4] } 5... Nb4 { [%cal Gb4d5,Gf6d5] } (5... Nxe4 6. Qe2 (6. Nxd4?! Bc5 { [%csl Rf2][%cal Rc5f2,Re4f2] } 7. c3) 6... f5 { Belgrade Gambit/Modern Defense } 7. Ng5 d3 8. cxd3 Nd4 9. Qh5+ g6 10. Qh4 c6 11. dxe4 cxd5 12. exd5 Bg7 13. Kd1 h6 14. Nf3 Qxh4 (14... Nxf3 15. Qxd8+ Kxd8 16. gxf3) 15. Nxh4 Kf7) (5... Bc5 6. Bg5 Be7) (5... Nxd5?! 6. exd5) (5... Be7 6. Bf4 (6. Nxd4) (6. Bc4) 6... d6 7. Nxd4 Nxd5 8. exd5 Nxd4 9. Qxd4) (5... Bb4+ 6. Nxb4 Nxb4 7. e5) 6. Bc4 Nbxd5 7. exd5 Bb4+ 8. Bd2 Qe7+ 9. Qe2 Bxd2+ 10. Kxd2 Qxe2+ 11. Kxe2 c5 12. dxc6 bxc6 13. Nxd4 d5 *


