{ This is a very subjective collection of exceptional games for the year 2017. }
1. a3 { What qualifies a game as "notable"? } 1... h6 { - An interesting novelty in opening theory (Aronian - Carlsen) } 2. b3 { - Surprising and successful sacrifices (Ider - Hou, Kramnik - Harikrishna) } 2... g6 { - Sharp, inspiring attacks (Lei - Zhai, Antal - Vorobiov) } 3. c3 { - And maybe more … } 3... f6 { No blitz or rapid games, no games with obvious blunders. } 4. d3 { If there is a video analysis, it is added as the first comment, before move 1. } 4... e6 { Some games are annotated already, some are still waiting for that. } 5. e3 { Please contact me, if you want to contribute — either by adding new games or by helping with annotations. } 5... d6 { If you like this study, please hit the ❤. :) } *


