1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Nf3 { E21 Nimzo-Indian Defense: Three Knights Variation } 4... O-O 5. Bg5 c5 6. e3 cxd4 7. Qxd4 Nc6 8. Qd3 h6 9. Bh4 d5 10. Rd1 g5 11. Bg3 Ne4 12. Nd2 Nc5 13. Qc2 d4 14. Nf3 e5 15. Nxe5 dxc3 16. Rxd8 cxb2+ 17. Ke2?? { (0.28 → -3.03) Blunder. Best move was Rd2. } (17. Rd2 Rd8 18. Nf3 Bg4 19. Qxb2 Bxf3 20. gxf3 Rxd2 21. Qxd2 Bxd2+ 22. Kxd2 Rd8+ 23. Ke2 Rd3) 17... Rxd8 18. Qxb2 Na4 19. Qc2?! { (-2.42 → -2.94) Inaccuracy. Best move was Qb3. } (19. Qb3 Nc3+ 20. Kf3 h5 21. h3 Bf5 22. Bf4 Ne4 23. Nxc6 Nd2+ 24. Kg3 Nxb3 25. Nxb4 h4+) 19... Nc3+ 20. Kf3 Rd4 21. h3 h5 22. Bh2? { (-2.67 → -4.43) Mistake. Best move was e4. } (22. e4 Rxe4 23. Qxe4 Nxe4 24. Kxe4 f5+ 25. Kd3 f4 26. Nxc6 Bf5+ 27. Kd4 bxc6 28. a3 Bxa3) 22... g4+ 23. Kg3 Rd2 24. Qb3?? { (-4.07 → -7.80) Blunder. Best move was Qxd2. } (24. Qxd2) 24... Ne4+ 25. Kh4? { (-7.54 → -11.58) Mistake. Best move was Kf4. } (25. Kf4 Rxf2+ 26. Nf3 gxf3 27. g4 Nd2 28. Qd3 Nxf1 29. Rxf1 Rxh2 30. gxh5 Bxh3 31. Rxf3 Be6) 25... Be7+ 26. Kxh5 Kg7? { (-10.97 → -8.08) Mistake. Best move was Rxf2. } (26... Rxf2 27. Bf4 Nxe5 28. Qb1 Bf5 29. Qxe4 Bxe4 30. Bxe5 gxh3 31. Kg4 f6 32. Bd4 hxg2 33. Bxg2) 27. Bf4? { (-8.08 → -11.24) Mistake. Best move was Nxc6. } (27. Nxc6 Bf5 28. Qc3+ f6 29. Bb8 Nxc3 30. Nxe7 Be6 31. f4 gxf3 32. gxf3 Rxb8 33. Rg1+ Kf7) 27... Bf5 28. Bh6+ Kh7 29. Qxb7 Rxf2 30. Bg5?! { (-10.17 → Mate in 7) Checkmate is now unavoidable. Best move was Qxe7. } (30. Qxe7 Nxe7 31. Rg1 Ng3+ 32. Kh4 Nxf1 33. Bf4 Ng6+ 34. Kg5 gxh3 35. Nf3 Nxf4 36. Kxf4 hxg2) 30... Rh8 31. Nxf7 Bg6+ 32. Kxg4 Ne5+ { White resigns. } 0-1


