{ The basic structure White wants to achieve. There is no fixed move order. The KIA is a system rather than an opening with specific move orders.

Despite the "Attack" in it's name, it's rather quiet in the first few moves, and Black can equalize early. } { [%cal Gf1e1,Ge4e5,Ga2a3,Gf2f4,Gd2f1] }
