 Nbd7 { Petrosian Variation/Normal Defense } 8. Bg5 h6 9. Bh4 g5 10. Bg3 Nh5 11. h4 { Petrosian Variation/Keres Defense })) 7... Nc6 { Orthodox Variation/Aronin-Taimanov Defense } (7... a5 { Orthodox Variation/Ukranian Defense }) (7... Na6 { Orthodox Variation/Glek Defense }) (7... c6 { Orthodox Variation/Donner Defense }) (7... Nbd7 { Orthodox Variation/Positional Defense } 8. d5 { Orthodox Variation/Positional Defense/Closed Line } (8. Re1 c6 9. Bf1 a5 { Orthodox Variation/Positional Defense/Main Line } (9... exd4 10. Nxd4)) (8. Be3)) 8. d5 Ne7 9. Ne1 { Orthodox Variation/Classical System } (9. Bd2 { Orthodox Variation/Korchnoi Attack }) (9. b4 { Orthodox Variation/Bayonet Attack } 9... a5 (9... Nh5 10. Qc2 { Orthodox Variation/Bayonet Attack/Yepishin's Line } (10. g3 f5 11. Ng5 Nf6 12. f3) (10. c5 Nf4 11. Bxf4 exf4 12. Rc1) (10. Re1 { Orthodox Variation/Bayonet Attack/Sokolov's Line } 10... f5 11. Ng5 Nf6 12. Bf3 c6)) 10. Ba3 (10. bxa5 Rxa5 11. Nd2) 10... axb4 11. Bxb4) 9... Nd7 10. Be3 { Orthodox Variation/Classical System/Neo-Classsical Line } (10. Nd3 f5 11. Bd2) (10. f3 f5 { Orthodox Variation/Classical System/Traditional Line } 11. g4 { Orthodox Variation/Classical System/Benko Attack }) 10... f5 11. f3 f4 12. Bf2 g5 13. Rc1 Ng6 14. c5 { Orthodox Variation/Classical System/Kozul Gambit } *


